General.Description: Nav Coin is a decentralized encryption that is built on top of the latest version of Bitcoin Core, with additional features and functionality. Nav Coin was generated to make online payments easy to carry at low cost and while ensuring your privacy.Nav coin has been publicly traded since July 2014. Nav Coin is traded on the largest Cryptocurrency transactions on the web. Nav Coin has a dedicated development team - whom we believe has given it some of the most exciting technology in the cryptocurrency market!
General.Features: The first feature, Faster Transaction Times: Allow sending the NAV anywhere on the planet immediately and have that verified spend in 30 seconds. The second feature, Earn While You Sleep: Thanks to Proof of Stake, you can earn up to 5% interest on your investment simply by transferring your money to staking mode. Finally, Optional Private Payments: Easy to send personal transactions encrypted through our blockchain powered NAVTech system.
General.Technology: Nav Coin is the first cryptocurrency to be completely anonymous. There are many anonymous coins, Nav Coin is different because its encryption software completely disconnects and randomizes transaction data, removing it even from an IP address. The anonymous system is built using the well-known bitcoins blockchain technology and uses a subchain to handle anonymous transactions.
